dc_title_s: Ringwood Manor, New Jersey 1962 brochure front
dc_creator_sm: New Jersey Department of Conservation and Economic Development
dc_description_s: Outside cover of brochure issued by the New Jersey Department of Conservation and Economic Development about Ringwood Manor State Park. Front of brochure features a table of campsites available and descriptions of the bathing facilities, cabin and boat rentals and hunting grounds. Two photographic illustrations.
